Class XCTextComponent

  • java.lang.Object
    • cz.syntea.xdef.component.XCTextComponent
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    XComponent

    public class XCTextComponent
extends java.lang.Object
implements XComponent
    Interface of XComponent (Java class generated from X-definitions according to a model of Element). Java source of the XComponent is possible to generate by GenXComponent.
